# The Algorithm

```
include necessary headers[stdio.h, unistd.h , etc..]

start main

    initialize terminal
        clear screen
        hide cursor
    
    initialize state
        declare any variables needed for animation

    start loop
        move cursor to draw position
        draw current frame
        flush output
        update state
        sleep
    end loop

    restore terminal
        show cursor

end main
```


The 4 steps to be executed every frame :
1. draw      — put something on screen
2. flush     — force terminal to show it
3. update    — change the state for next frame
4. sleep     — control speed

